Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:56.24,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}包羅萬象什麼的 無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:58.41,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}腦袋裡面載入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:00.54,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}是不是不可能的嘛
Comment: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.38,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Go ask my instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:23.72,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直響著的沉默的警鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:25.94,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那又是誰的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:28.54,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不要迷茫跳進去跳進去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.54,0:01:30.90,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}站起來 破壞掉這無理的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:32.49,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果解不開這沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:34.91,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就大喊露鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:37.24,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到終幕我都要說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:40.11,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Gear up! 這不是玩笑
